content.Query:
ContainerLog
 | extend _data = parse_json(LogEntry)
 | sort by TimeGenerated desc
 | extend senderIP = tostring(_data.remoteHost)
 | extend sender=tostring(case(senderIP startswith "10.241", "canary", senderIP startswith "10.244", "orbital", "unknown"))
 | project TimeGenerated, senderIP, sender, subsystem=tostring(_data.subsystem), event=tostring(_data.event), message=tostring(_data.message), filename=tostring(_data.filename), mb=todouble(_data.fileSizeInKB)/1000, seconds=todouble(_data.durationInSeconds), containerName=tostring(_data.containerName), error=tostring(_data.error)
 | where event=="complete"
 | where subsystem == "tcp-to-blob"
//  | where message=="✅ BLOB upload complete."
 | summarize count=dcount(message) by message, bin(TimeGenerated,15m)

ContainerLog 
 | extend _data = parse_json(LogEntry) 
 | sort by TimeGenerated desc 
 | extend senderIP = tostring(_data.remoteHost) 
 | extend sender=tostring(case(senderIP startswith "10.241" or _data.subsystem endswith 'canary', "canary", senderIP startswith "10.244", "orbital", "unknown")) 
 | project TimeGenerated, senderIP, sender, subsystem=tostring(_data.subsystem), event=tostring(_data.event), message=tostring(_data.message), filename=tostring(_data.filename), mb=todouble(_data.fileSizeInKB)/1000, seconds=todouble(_data.durationInSeconds), containerName=tostring(_data.containerName), error=tostring(_data.error) 
 | where event=="complete" 
 | where message=="✅ BLOB upload complete." 
 | summarize ['max time']=max(seconds/60), ['min time']=min(seconds/60) by bin(TimeGenerated,4hr)

ContainerLog 
  | extend _data = parse_json(LogEntry) 
  | sort by TimeGenerated desc 
  | extend senderIP = tostring(_data.remoteHost) 
  | extend sender=tostring(case(senderIP startswith "10.241", "canary", senderIP startswith "10.244", "orbital", "unknown")) 
  | project TimeGenerated, senderIP, sender, subsystem=tostring(_data.subsystem), event=tostring(_data.event), message=tostring(_data.message), filename=tostring(_data.filename), mb=todouble(_data.fileSizeInKB)/1000, seconds=todouble(_data.durationInSeconds), containerName=tostring(_data.containerName), error=tostring(_data.error) 
  | where event=="complete" 
 | where message=="✅ BLOB upload complete." 
  | summarize ['mb/second']=min(mb/seconds) by bin(TimeGenerated,4hr)

ContainerLog 
 | extend _data = parse_json(LogEntry) 
 | sort by TimeGenerated desc 
 | extend senderIP = tostring(_data.remoteHost) 
 | extend sender=tostring(case(senderIP startswith "10.241", "canary", senderIP startswith "10.244", "orbital", "unknown")) 
 | project TimeGenerated, senderIP, sender, subsystem=tostring(_data.subsystem), event=tostring(_data.event), message=tostring(_data.message), filename=tostring(_data.filename), mb=todouble(_data.fileSizeInKB)/1000, seconds=todouble(_data.durationInSeconds), containerName=tostring(_data.containerName), error=tostring(_data.error) 
 | where event=="complete" 
 | where message=="✅ BLOB upload complete." 
 | summarize ['mb']=max(mb) by bin(TimeGenerated,15m)

ContainerLog
 | extend _data = parse_json(LogEntry)
 | sort by TimeGenerated desc
 | extend senderIP = tostring(_data.remoteHost)
 | extend sender=tostring(case(senderIP startswith "10.241", "canary", senderIP startswith "10.244", "orbital", "unknown"))
 | project TimeGenerated, senderIP, sender, subsystem=tostring(_data.subsystem), event=tostring(_data.event), message=tostring(_data.message), filename=tostring(_data.filename), mb=todouble(_data.fileSizeInKB)/1000, seconds=todouble(_data.durationInSeconds), containerName=tostring(_data.containerName), error=tostring(_data.error)
 | where event=="complete"
 | where message=="✅ BLOB upload complete."
 | summarize count=dcount(filename) by bin(TimeGenerated,15m)

ContainerLog
| extend _data = parse_json(LogEntry)
| sort by TimeGenerated desc
| extend senderIP = tostring(_data.remoteHost)
| extend sender=tostring(case(senderIP startswith "10.241", "canary", senderIP startswith "10.244", "orbital", "unknown"))
| project TimeGenerated, senderIP, sender, subsystem=tostring(_data.subsystem), event=tostring(_data.event), message=tostring(_data.message), filename=tostring(_data.filename), mb=todouble(_data.fileSizeInKB)/1000, seconds=todouble(_data.durationInSeconds), containerName=tostring(_data.containerName), error=tostring(_data.error)
| where event=="complete"
| where message=="✅ BLOB upload complete."
| top-nested 10 of sender  by mb=sum(mb)

ContainerLog
| extend _data = parse_json(LogEntry)
| sort by TimeGenerated desc
| extend senderIP = tostring(_data.remoteHost)
| extend sender=tostring(case(senderIP startswith "10.241", "canary", senderIP startswith "10.244", "orbital", "unknown"))
| project TimeGenerated, senderIP, sender, subsystem=tostring(_data.subsystem), event=tostring(_data.event), message=tostring(_data.message), filename=tostring(_data.filename), _mb=todouble(_data.fileSizeInKB)/1000, seconds=todouble(_data.durationInSeconds), containerName=tostring(_data.containerName), error=tostring(_data.error)
| where event=="complete"
| where message=="✅ BLOB upload complete."
| summarize mb=sum(_mb) by bin(TimeGenerated,15m)
